                      "body": "The IDS to EDW Member Supplemental Benefit process can not run while there is another process listed on the P_RUN_CYC as running.\n\nSource = IDS\nTarget =  EDW\nSubj = \"MBR BENEFIT_SUPLMNT\"\nFrequency = Daily",
                      "blobFilenames": "",
                      "fromemail": {
                        "value": "@pipeline().globalParameters.gbl_param_fromemail",
                        "type": "Expression"
                      },
                      "containerName": ""
                    }
                  }
                }
              ]
